Package: ethercat-igh
Architecture: any
Depends: dkms, ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: IgH EtherCAT Master with DKMS kernel module support
 IgH EtherCAT Master userspace tools, libraries, systemd services,
 configuration files, and DKMS kernel module source.
 .
 Kernel modules (ec_master, ec_generic, ec_igb and others) are
 automatically built via DKMS for the running kernel on install
 and on every kernel update.
